### Test Simulator Configuration API Endpoints
### Use VS Code REST Client extension or similar to test these endpoints

@simulatorUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Get current simulator status
GET {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/status

### Get current simulator configuration
GET {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/config

### ======================================
### Order Generator Configuration Tests
### ======================================

### Update order configuration - Low volume
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/config/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "intervalMinutes": 120,
  "minOrdersPerInterval": 1,
  "maxOrdersPerInterval": 2
}

### Update order configuration - Medium volume
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/config/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "intervalMinutes": 60,
  "minOrdersPerInterval": 2,
  "maxOrdersPerInterval": 5
}

### Update order configuration - High volume (AI agent challenge)
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/config/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "intervalMinutes": 10,
  "minOrdersPerInterval": 5,
  "maxOrdersPerInterval": 15
}

### Reset order configuration to defaults
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/config/orders/reset

