### ======================================
### Validation Tests (should return errors)
### ======================================

### Invalid interval (too short)
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/config/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "intervalMinutes": 0,
  "minOrdersPerInterval": 1,
  "maxOrdersPerInterval": 3
}

### Invalid interval (too long)
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/config/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "intervalMinutes": 2000,
  "minOrdersPerInterval": 1,
  "maxOrdersPerInterval": 3
}

### Invalid volume (min > max)
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/config/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "intervalMinutes": 60,
  "minOrdersPerInterval": 10,
  "maxOrdersPerInterval": 5
}

### Invalid volume (exceeds max)
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/config/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "intervalMinutes": 10,
  "minTicketsPerInterval": 5,
  "maxTicketsPerInterval": 100
}

