### ======================================
### Stress Test Mode (Still available)
### ======================================

### Enable stress test mode (high volume tickets only)
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/stresstest/enable

### Check stress test status
GET {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/stresstest/status

### Disable stress test mode
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/stresstest/disable

### Reset stress test mode to config defaults
POST {{simulatorUrl}}/api/simulator/stresstest/reset
